name: TerrAscend Corp.
longDescription: TerrAscend Corp is a company focused on creating and delivering quality cannabis products and services that meet the evolving needs of patients. It also provides education and support programs to physicians and patients through healthcare professionals. It has one operating segment, being cultivation, production, and sale of cannabis products, with subsidiaries located in Canada and the United States.
